{"tid":1062451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 蘋果的iCloud服務出現大面積癱瘓：持續超4小時","createTime":"2019-03-15T06:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T06:47:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d79067ecec0d96dc596e31362a180f8b79ad1ef9","tid":1062451,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T06:02:09.000Z","msg":"據美國科技媒體AppleInsider報導，蘋果雲服務出現宕機事件，包括Apple新聞，照片，找到我的iPhone（查找我的iPhone）及許多關鍵iCloud功能受到影響。<br />\n蘋果系統狀態（Apple System Status）頁面顯示，多種蘋果線上服務無法全負荷運行。問題從美東時間週四14日上午11點開始出現（北京時間晚上23點），直到下午3點28分修復（北京時間15日凌晨3點28分）.AppleInsider認為，從多種跡象看，應該是核心出現問題，並不是許多小問題在同一時間發生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wo2hUWW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWo2hUWW.png&h=478e967a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/414/459.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F414%2F459.htm&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=5dd64330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/414/459.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3dd37794aba7c094472bfb21ed5d17c43e52206c","tid":1062451,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T06:02:27.000Z","msg":"輪到apple<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91bb70de233ad67160d6e5f74cfd1b4b55085110","tid":1062451,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T06:02:49.000Z","msg":"World no IT不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a70c3f835ed24aa797683283a9cb4b679d4dc00","tid":1062451,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T06:05:21.000Z","msg":"google fb apple呢幾日發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\